* Overall better optimized than VRshat;
* Content is not locked under a subscription paywall. You only pay for the full game once and that's it;
* Developers actually encourages use and development of mods, unlike VRshat where they locked the use of mods (like QoL mods) just so they can sell their own "solution" on their subscription service;
* Developers have also been very active in the fixing of bugs and general improvement of the service after "the great exodus";
* Has optional "nude patch" that you can download as free DLC. You can now disable kids and enable tities!

Overall, ChilloutVR have been improving a lot after the influx of new players. I would personally like to congratulate the VRshat devs for helping improve this game. It was so kind of them to help the competition by sabotaging their own game so they don't have the monopoly anymore. Thank you VRshat devs, this would not have been possible withouth you!

