I Chilled in a few familiar worlds and a few new ones,  Meeting and greeting a bunch of chill, laid back people; 
flew around and through the walls using the built-in game functions;
Found a world that tells you you need EMM to experience it fully;
and noticed the graphics just looked a bit better in general.

Give these guys the time to increase their server and bandwidth and this is going to be a VRC killer.  Its the same, but better.

